msgstr "Tamaños de muestra de grupo de al menos %1$s y %2$s, respectivamente"

msgid ""
"On the other hand, if %1$s%2$s, the evidence would exceed the criterion "
"&mdash; and hence we would correctly claim that %3$s &mdash; at least %4$s%% "
